{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC09_ERN_140.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x22,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "I've always thought this, but...Ernie, you're such a nice person."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh? What are you saying all of a sudden? Are you trying to get something out of me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "That's just what I think. You're always so nice to me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "And to Tanya, and everyone else, without showing more favor to anyone."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x126,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, well you could say that I'm everyone's friend. Although, I'm not really conscious of it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "It's probably just in your nature. Ernie, you're a good person."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x128,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Oh, but still, if I do something good, word of it might go around and it could lead to more business for me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... Well, I guess you could put it that way..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hmhmhm, I guess it's time to reveal this to you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I'm actually...a pretty bad person."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "This kindness is all just an act, and I've actually calculated everything out."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I make calculations to ensure that my kindness will be rewarded by having more business."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "You just came up with that, didn't you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Th-That's not true. I really might be a bad person."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Why are you pretending to be a bad person all of a sudden?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x5f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "H-How can you be sure that I'm just pretending to be a bad person?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Because you're always smiling. See? You're even doing it now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "No matter how I look at it, that can't be the face of someone who's thinking about bad things."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x61,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I guess I can't pull it off. I've always admired the image of \"bad guys.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x102,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "With their sharp eyes, ever alert, and on top of that, they have mustaches!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "So it's the mustache..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x108,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Yup. For me, a mustache is a must. It looks cool and wild."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x109,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Glasses would be cool, too. And wearing a coat, smoking cigarettes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "(I feel like this image is getting closer and closer to Mr. Keith...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x10a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I've thought about all this since I was little, so..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I've always admired men that're cool and bad..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Ernie, you're totally not like that, so I don't think that's possible for you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "You're right. I guess I can't do bad things. I'll keep on living like I've always been..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "D-Don't get so depressed."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Well...don't you think, as a merchant, I lack a certain appeal?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "I don't think so. I think you're perfect just the way you are right now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "I see. If you say so, then maybe it's okay for me to stay like this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "(I think he's wonderful just the way he is, but...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "(I never knew Ernie admired those kinds of people...)"
        }
    ]
}